sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CalendarApp as Calendar Application (e.g., Google, Outlook)
    participant SyncService as Sync & Integration Service
    participant CRM as CRM System (e.g., Salesforce, HubSpot)

    title Calendar Sync Flow with CRM

    User->>SyncService: Authorize Calendar Access
    SyncService-->>CalendarApp: Request OAuth/API Access
    CalendarApp-->>User: User grants permission
    User->>SyncService: Authorize CRM Access
    SyncService-->>CRM: Request OAuth/API Access
    CRM-->>User: User grants permission
    SyncService->>SyncService: Store API Keys / Access Tokens

    Note over User,CRM: Ongoing Synchronization

    alt Event Creation/Update in Calendar
        User->>CalendarApp: Create/Update Calendar Event
        CalendarApp->>SyncService: Notify of Event Change (Webhook/Polling)
        SyncService->>CalendarApp: Fetch Event Details (Attendees, Time, Description)
        SyncService->>SyncService: Process Event Data & Identify CRM Contacts
        SyncService->>CRM: Create/Update Activity/Event in CRM
        CRM-->>SyncService: Activity/Event ID Confirmation
        SyncService-->>CalendarApp: (Optional) Add CRM Link to Event Description
        CalendarApp-->>User: Event updated in Calendar
    else Event Deletion in Calendar
        User->>CalendarApp: Delete Calendar Event
        CalendarApp->>SyncService: Notify of Event Deletion
        SyncService->>CRM: Locate & Delete Corresponding Activity/Event in CRM
        CRM-->>SyncService: Deletion Confirmation
    end

    alt Activity Creation/Update in CRM
        User->>CRM: Create/Update CRM Activity (e.g., Meeting)
        CRM->>SyncService: Notify of Activity Change (Webhook/Polling)
        SyncService->>CRM: Fetch Activity Details (Attendees, Time, Description)
        SyncService->>SyncService: Process Activity Data & Map to Calendar Users
        SyncService->>CalendarApp: Create/Update Calendar Event
        CalendarApp-->>SyncService: Event ID Confirmation
        SyncService-->>CRM: (Optional) Add Calendar Link to Activity Description
        CRM-->>User: Activity updated in CRM
    else Activity Deletion in CRM
        User->>CRM: Delete CRM Activity
        CRM->>SyncService: Notify of Activity Deletion
        SyncService->>CalendarApp: Locate & Delete Corresponding Calendar Event
        CalendarApp-->>SyncService: Deletion Confirmation
    end

    SyncService->>SyncService: Log Sync Status & Errors
    SyncService-->>User: (Optional) Notify User of Sync Issues